Package com.google.caliper.config

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaliperConfig
    Represents caliper configuration.
    CaliperConfigLoader
    Loads caliper configuration files and, if necessary, creates new versions from the defaults.
    ConfigModule
    Bindings for Caliper configuration.
    InstrumentConfig
    This is the configuration passed to the instrument by the user.
    ResultProcessorConfig
    This is the configuration passed to the ResultProcessor by the user.
    VmConfig
    This is the configuration passed to the VM by the user.
    VmConfig.Builder  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidConfigurationException
    Thrown when an invalid configuration has been specified by the user.
